dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Waukesha County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right of Ways (ROW) for Waukesha County, Wisconsin in 2020. The follwing features and tables are included: 'WAUKESHA_ROADS_2020', 'WAUKESHA_ROW_2020' and 'WAUKESHA_ROADALIASTABLE_2020'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://data-waukeshacounty.opendata.arcgis.com/
